cloudflare-log-collector (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Polls Cloudflare GraphQL Analytics API for firewall events and HTTP traffic
  * Ships events to Loki as structured JSON log lines
  * Exposes Prometheus metrics for poll health and traffic stats
  * OpenTelemetry tracing with log-trace correlation

